    <title>Crossfeed</title>
    <p>Easy Effects uses the Crossfeed by bs2b. This plugin is used to improve headphone listening of stereo audio records. It does so by mixing the left and right channel in a way that simulates a stereo speaker setup while using headphones.</p>
